            <h4>About BareProx</h4>
            <p>
                <strong>BareProx</strong> automates backup, restore, and snapshot management for Proxmox environments using integrated NetApp storage. This platform aims to simplify VM data protection, recovery, and storage operations for administrators.
            </p>

